{"version":1,"entries":{"person_5921859_translations":{"at":1773676794418,"data":{"id":5921859,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"强国铭","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Qiang Guoming","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"強國銘","primary":false}}]}},"person_5972888_translations":{"at":1773676803264,"data":{"id":5972888,"translations":[]}},"person_2496576_translations":{"at":1773676803422,"data":{"id":2496576,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Richie Koh was first discovered on Channel U’s campus talent hunt show Hey Gorgeous 2013 where he emerged as the runner-up for the season. He graduated with a Diploma in Financial Informatics from Ngee Ann Polytechnic, had always wanted to be an actor. He had to put that dream on hold until after his National Service in 2016.\n\nRichie’s stellar performances in various local drama series such as When Duty Calls 《卫国先锋》, 118 Reunion《118 大团圆》 and Divided 《分裂》 had left a lasting impression on viewers. These landed him his first nomination for “Best Newcomer” in Star Awards 2018.\n\nRiding on his increasing recognition and popularity among the masses, he moved on to a bigger arena by acting in movies where he performed equally well. His role as the gangster leader in the movie Wonderful! Liang Xi Mei 《旺得福梁细妹》 earned him praises from Singaporean director Jack Neo, and garnered rave reviews from both local and Malaysian fans. Shortly after, he was placed in the spotlight again with his outstanding performance in director Gilbert Chan’s horror movie 23:59: The Haunting Hour 《23:59 猛鬼兵营》.  He proves himself as an artiste of great acting and versatility and this landed him into leading roles for two movies - The Diam Diam Era directed by Jack Neo which has released in 2020 and 2021 and The Fatekeepers which is slated to release in 2022.\n\nWith his strong experiences in acting, he is all ready to take on more challenges and get on a bigger international platform in the regional market.","name":"Richie Koh","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Richie Koh","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"SG","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1993年6月16日—），新加坡新生代影视男演员，现为新传媒私人有限公司旗下全方位经纪合约男艺人。2013年参加《校园美魔王》踏入演艺圈。\n\n2017年，电视剧《卫国先锋》。2019年，参演《游乐场》及《离归》。2022年，参演《你的世界我们懂》，饰演特殊人士郑天才，并以此角色首次入围最佳男主角即得奖。","name":"许瑞奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1993年6月16日—），新加坡新生代影视男演员，现为新传媒私人有限公司旗下全方位经纪合约男艺人。2013年参加《校园美魔王》踏入演艺圈。\n\n2017年，电视剧《卫国先锋》。2019年，参演《游乐场》及《离归》。\n\n2022年，参演《你的世界我们懂》，饰演特殊人士郑天才，并以此角色首次入围最佳男主角即得奖。","name":"许瑞奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1993 年 6 月 16 日—），新加坡新生代影視男演員，現為新傳媒私人有限公司旗下全方位經紀合約男藝人。2013 年參加《校園美魔王》踏入演藝圈。\n\n2017 年，電視劇《衞國先鋒》。2019 年，參演《遊樂場》及《離歸》。\n\n2022 年，參演《你的世界我們懂》，飾演特殊人士鄭天才，並以此角色首次入圍最佳男主角即得獎。","name":"許瑞奇","primary":false}}]}},"tv_19389_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773676804528,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/hmNnPkaAfWWcHMUnQVzYsswZysI.jpg","created_by":[{"id":1163180,"credit_id":"5dec59316d000c001255104e","name":"Leung Tin","original_name":"Leung Tin","gender":2,"profile_path":"/Ag0NhBeUpxp0XQerRqWfhOxZHgJ.jpg"}],"episode_run_time":[45],"first_air_date":"1998-11-30","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"},{"id":10765,"name":"Sci-Fi & Fantasy"}],"homepage":"https://web.archive.org/web/20110424230959/http://www.hkatv.com/drama/vampire/","id":19389,"in_production":false,"languages":["cn"],"last_air_date":"2005-11-08","last_episode_to_air":{"id":2067296,"name":"Episode 11","