ginal_name":"Howard Cummings","popularity":0.5153,"profile_path":"/wdfpweH5G6FLoADbBEgjEC9zfJC.jpg","credit_id":"66175a640a517c0163ff6a01","department":"Production","job":"Co-Producer"}],"id":106379}},"person_55258_translations":{"at":1773676841965,"data":{"id":55258,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Robinne Lee is an American actress and author. She made her screen debut in the 1997 independent film Hav Plenty, and later has appeared in films National Security (2003), Deliver Us from Eva (2003), Hitch (2005), Seven Pounds (2008), Fifty Shades Darker (2017), and Fifty Shades Freed (2018).","name":"Robinne Lee","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"罗宾·李（Robinne Lee）是美国女演员和作家。她在 1997 年的独立电影《Hav Plenty》中首次亮相银幕，后来出演了电影《国家安全》（2003 年）、《从伊娃那里拯救我们》（2003 年）、《搭便车》（2005 年）、《七磅》（2008 年）、《五十度黑暗》（2017 年）和《五十度自由》（2018 年）。","name":"罗宾·李","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"羅賓·李（Robinne Lee）是美國女演員和作家。她在 1997 年的獨立電影《Hav Plenty》中首次亮相銀幕，後來出演了電影《國家安全》（2003 年）、《從伊娃那裏拯救我們》（2003 年）、《搭便車》（2005 年）、《救人七命》（2008 年）、《五十度黑暗》（2017 年）和《五十度自由》（2018 年）。","name":"羅賓·李","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Робінн Лі","primary":false}}]}},"person_553983_translations":{"at":1773676842822,"data":{"id":553983,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Trishalee Hardy","primary":true}}]}},"person_56356_translations":{"at":1773676847461,"data":{"id":56356,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Gina Philips (born May 10, 1970) is an American actress. Philips was born Gina Consolo in Miami Beach, Florida. She is known for her recurring roles on David E. Kelley's Ally McBeal as Sandy Hingle and Boston Public as Jenna Miller. Her film credits include Jeepers Creepers, Love & Debate, The Anarchist Cookbook, Dead and Breakfast and The Sick House. In addition, Philips has made guest appearances on Star Trek: DS9, Sliders, ER, CSI, Medium and Monk. She has also starred in Rubi Zack's 2006 Ring Around the Rosie.","name":"Gina Philips","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Gina Philips (* 10. Mai 1970 in Miami Beach, Florida; gebürtig Gina Consolo) ist eine US-amerikanische Schauspielerin und Filmproduzentin.\n\nPhilips studierte an der University of Pennsylvania, brach jedoch ihr Studium kurz vor dem Abschluss ab. Sie debütierte als Schauspielerin in einer Folge der Fernsehserie Unser lautes Heim aus dem Jahr 1992. Im Thriller Ermordet am 16. Juli (1993) spielte sie an der Seite von Ally Walker und Martin Sheen eine kleine Nebenrolle. Im Independent-Musical Rave, Dancing to a Different Beat (1994) war sie in einer der größeren Rollen zu sehen, eine größere Rolle übernahm sie auch im Filmdrama Zeit der Bewährung (1995). Im Fernsehthriller Angriff der Killerbienen (1995) trat sie neben Ryan Phillippe auf. Im für das Fernsehen produzierte Krimidrama Bella Mafia (1997) spielte Philips neben Vanessa Redgrave, Dennis Farina, Nastassja Kinski, Jennifer Tilly, Illeana Douglas und James Marsden. In den Jahren 1999 bis 2000 spielte sie in der Fernsehserie Ally McBeal die Rolle von Sandy Hingle. Im Horrorfilm Jeepers Creepers (2001) übernahm sie neben dem ihren Bruder verkörpernden Justin Long eine der Hauptrollen. Im Kurzfilm Something More (2003) spielte Philips an der Seite von Tony Shalhoub und Jeremy Sisto; außerdem war sie als Produzentin tätig. In der von ihr produzierten Komödie Thanks to Gravity (2006) spielte sie die Hauptrolle.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吉娜·菲利普斯（Gina Philips，1970年5月10日-），美国女演员。","name":"吉娜·菲利普斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジーナ・フィリップス","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吉娜·菲利普斯（Gina Philips，1970 年 5 月 10 日-），美國女演員。","name":"吉娜·菲利普斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джина Филипс","primary":false}}]}},"person_4023329_translations":{"at":1773676862458,"data":{"id":4023329,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Phương Bình","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Phương Bình","primary":true}}]}},"person_588057_translations":{"at":1773676865298,"data":{"id":588057,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Bai Baihe is a Chinese actress. She is known for her breakout role in the 2011 romantic-comedy Love is Not Blind, also starring Wen Zhang. The low-budget film became a surprise hit and end up grossing over 350 million yuan at the Chinese boxoffice. In 2013, she starred in the romantic comedy A Wedding Invitation opposite Eddie Peng.\n\nBai was married to Chinese actor and singer Yufan Chen from 2006-2015. They have a son together Chen Shengtong born in 2008.","name":"Bai Baihe","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"白百何，本名白雪，演员、配音、制片，毕业于中央戏剧学院表演系本科班。\n\n2006年，因主演首部电视剧《与青春有关的日子》而进入演艺圈。2011年，凭借治愈系爱情电影《失恋33天》被观众熟知，并获得第31届大众电影百花奖最佳女主角奖，同时她还提名第49届台湾电影金马奖最佳女主角和第15届中国电影华表奖优秀女演员。2012年，因主演职场剧《浮沉》提名第19届上海电视节白玉兰奖最佳女演员。2013年，凭借爱情片《被偷走的那五年》入围第16届上海国际电影节最佳女演员，同年主演喜剧电影《私人订制》。\n\n2015年1月，主演青春励志情感剧《长大》；6月，成立白百何工作室；随后凭借奇幻电影《捉妖记》获得第13届中国长春电影节最佳女主角奖；同年，她还因励志电影《滚蛋吧！肿瘤君》获得第16届中国电影华表奖优秀女演员奖、第7届中国电影导演协会年度女演员和第23届北京大学生电影节最佳女演员。2016年，凭借剧情电影《火锅英雄》获得第8届澳大利亚国际华语电影节最佳女演员奖；同年，她还获得中国电影国际传播突出贡献人物奖。2017年，主演警匪动作电影《绑架者》、都市医疗行业励志剧《外科风云》。2018年，主演电影《捉妖记2》。2019年主演电影《妈阁是座城》，并凭借该电影提名第32届中国电影金鸡奖最佳女主角奖。2022年，主演都市剧《欢迎光临》播出。","name":"白百何","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"바이바이허는 중국의 배우이다. 어린 시절부터 노래, 춤, 연기에 재능을 보였고 12세 시절에는 베이징 무도 학원에 입학했다. 2000년에는 장이머우 감독의 영화 《행복한 날들》의 오디션에 참가했지만 탈락했다.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"白百何","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bạch Bách Hà","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"白百何，本名白雪，演員、配音、製片，畢業於中央戲劇學院表演系本科班。\n\n2006 年，因主演首部電視劇《與青春有關的日子》而進入演藝圈。2011 年，憑藉治癒系愛情電影《失戀 33 天》被觀眾熟知，並獲得第 31 屆大眾電影百花獎最佳女主角獎，同時她還提名第 49 屆台灣 電影金馬獎最佳女主角和第 15 屆中國電影華表獎優秀女演員。2012 年，因主演職場劇《浮沉》提名第 19 屆上海電視節白玉蘭獎最佳女演員。2013 年，憑藉愛情片《被偷走的那五年》入圍第 16 屆上海國際電影節最佳女演員，同年主演喜劇電影《私人訂制》。\n\n2015 年 1 月，主演青春勵志情感劇《飛越未來》；6 月，成立白百何工作室；隨後憑藉奇幻電影《捉妖記》獲得第 13 屆中國長春電影節最佳女主角獎；同年，她還因勵志電影《滾蛋吧！腫瘤君》獲得第 16 屆中國電影華表獎優秀女演員獎、第 7 屆中國電影導演協會年度女演員和第 23 屆北京大學生電影節最佳女演員。2016 年，憑藉劇情電影《火鍋英雄》獲得第 8 屆澳大利亞國際華語電影節最佳女演員獎；同年，她還獲得中國電影國際傳播突出貢獻人物獎。2017 年，主演警匪動作電影《綁架者》、都市醫療行業勵志劇《外科風雲》。2018 年，主演電影《捉妖記 2》。2019 年主演電影《媽閣是座城》，並憑藉該電影提名第 32 屆中國電影金雞獎最佳女主角獎。2022 年，主演都市劇《歡迎光臨》播出。","name":"白百何","primary":false}}]}},"person_1410478_translations":{"at":1773676867931,"data":{"id":1410478,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"William Jackson Harper (born William Fitzgerald Harper; February 8, 1980), is an American actor. He portrayed Chidi Anagonye on the NBC comedy The Good Place (2016–2020).","name":"William Jackson Harper","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"윌리엄 잭슨 하퍼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"William Fitzgerald Harper, bekannt als William Jackson Harper (* 8. Februar 1980 in Dallas, Texas) ist ein US-amerikanischer Schauspieler.\n\nNach seinem Studium spielte er in mehreren kleinen Rollen mit und hatte 2007 seinen ersten Auftritt in Law & Order: Criminal Intent als Chayne Danforth. Zwischen 2009 und 2011 hatte er seine erste Hauptrolle in der Kinderserie The Electric Company. Seinen ersten Broadway-Auftritt hatte Harper im Jahr 2014 als James Harrison und Stokely Carmichael in dem Stück All The Way. Seit 2016 verkörpert er die Hauptrolle Chidi Anagonye in der Serie The Good Place. Bevor er die Rolle bekam, überlegte er, mit dem Schauspielern aufzuhören. Obwohl er anfangs nicht genau wusste, worum es in der Serie eigentlich ging, erhielt er für seinen Auftritt weitgehend positive Kritiken.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ウィリアム・ジャクソン・ハーパー","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ויליאם ג'קסון הרפר","primary":false}