006). In 2018, she starred in the Netflix Original crime drama series Seven Seconds.\n\nFrom Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia","name":"Clare-Hope Ashitey","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克莱尔-霍普·阿什蒂（Clare-Hope Ashitey，1987年2月12日-），英国女演员。她曾就读于索斯盖特的中央舞台表演艺术学校，同时在位于伦敦埃德蒙顿地区的拉蒂默学校接受教育七年。\n\n她花了一年的时间在学校和大学之间拍摄电影《男人的孩子》（2006）。2018年，她出演了Netflix原创犯罪剧集《七秒》。","name":"克莱尔-霍普·阿什蒂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克萊爾 - 霍普·阿什蒂（Clare - Hope Ashitey，1987 年 2 月 12 日-），英國女演員。她曾就讀於索斯蓋特的中央舞台表演藝術學校，同時在位於倫敦埃德蒙頓地區的拉蒂默學校接受教育七年。\n\n她花了一年的時間在學校和大學之間拍攝電影《男人的孩子》（2006）。2018 年，她出演了 Netflix 原創犯罪劇集《七秒》。","name":"克萊爾 - 霍普·阿什蒂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Клэр-Хоуп Эшити","primary":false}}]}},"person_3962326_translations":{"at":1773676915516,"data":{"id":3962326,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tahsin Lale","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tahsin Lale","primary":true}}]}},"person_1535199_translations":{"at":1773676917152,"data":{"id":1535199,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jan-Kau Wong","primary":false}}]}},"person_1191274_translations":{"at":1773676921338,"data":{"id":1191274,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sylvia Camarda","prima